Long-serving Nation Media Group Advertising Director Michael Ngugi has retired after 16 years at the company. Mr Ngugi joined the company in 2002 as the Head of Circulation and Distribution where he served for four years. He was then promoted to General Manager Advertising in 2004. In a statement, the company praised him for his dedication, contribution to its success and building a good team. Mr Tom Mshindi, the Editor-in-Chief, said the group was "very grateful for Mr Ngugi's service, he has done a fantastic job over the years and we wish him well."